  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.webm?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.mp4?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demon Hunters</strong> is a dynamic 2D action game with RPG elements, inspired by  classic action rpg games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.webm?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.mp4?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore randomly generated dungeons, battle hordes of demons, and defeat powerful bosses to seal the portal and save the kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.webm?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.mp4?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When darkness engulfed the royal castle, an ancient order of Demon Hunters sent three heroes — a <strong>Knight</strong>, a <strong>Pirate</strong>, and a <strong>Mage</strong> — on a deadly mission. Their goal is to destroy the four Lords of Darkness, claim their artifacts, and forever close the gates of Hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/474d2b839efd91b0d846efca6fac2cfe.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/474d2b839efd91b0d846efca6fac2cfe.webm?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/474d2b839efd91b0d846efca6fac2cfe.mp4?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Three heroes — three combat styles:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knight</strong> — strength and heavy armor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pirate</strong> — agility and precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mage</strong> — destructive spells and control.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What awaits you:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dangerous levels across unique biomes filled with enemies and traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil epic bosses and mini-bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon and Armor upgrades through traders in the castle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeons that change with every run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense and rewarding combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 Upgrade your hero, collect all the artifacts, and stop the demonic invasion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/49629a4569fc038c73817545887725ac.avif?t=1774366674\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.webm?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.mp4?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demon Hunters</strong> is a dynamic 2D action game with RPG elements, inspired by  classic action rpg games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.webm?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.mp4?t=1774366674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore randomly generated dungeons, battle hordes of demons, and defeat powerful bosses to seal the portal and save the kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.poster.avif?t=1774366674\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/