s through traders in the castle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeons that change with every run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense and rewarding combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 Upgrade your hero, collect all the artifacts, and stop the demonic invasion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/49629a4569fc038c73817545887725ac.avif?t=1774366674\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>",
